'''可食用水球'''是指由[[藻类植物|藻类植物]]的凝胶制成的类似球体的水容器。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.fastcompany.com/40403025/this-edible-water-bottle-is-how-youll-drink-in-the-future|title=This Edible Water Bottle Is How You’ll Drink In The Future|last1=Peters|first1=Adele|website=Fast Company|publisher=Fast Company|accessdate=25 March 2020|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112043039/https://www.fastcompany.com/40403025/this-edible-water-bottle-is-how-youll-drink-in-the-future|dead-url=no}}</ref>这种[[可再生|可再生]]包装是由[[Skipping_Rocks_Lab|Skipping Rocks Lab]]创建的，目的是为代替[[宝特瓶|一次性塑料瓶]]而提供更加“[[环境友善|环境友善]]”的替代品。<ref>{{Cite web|title = Ooho! the edible water bottle|url = http://www.skippingrockslab.com|website = www.skippingrocksla.com|accessdate = 2015-11-28|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151208140733/http://www.skippingrockslab.com/|archivedate = 2015-12-08|df = |dead-url = no}}</ref>该容器的创建者将其命名为“Ooho”，制作方法就是在由[[藻类|藻类]]和[[氯化钙|氯化钙]]制成的膜中封入少量水。制造过程包含在[[知识共享许可协议|知识共享许可协议]]中，因此任何人都可以免费使用该配方。 <ref>{{Cite web|url = https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kIXkGdEIB-o|title = Ooho|date = |accessdate = |website = |publisher = |last = García González|first = Rodrigo|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160310132528/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kIXkGdEIB-o|archivedate = 2016-03-10|df = |dead-url = no}}</ref>

== 传统水容器==
在美国，每年都有五百亿个一次性塑料瓶被生产，它们大多由[[聚对苯二甲酸乙二酯|聚对苯二甲酸乙二酯]] (PET) 制成，并且大多数被直接丢弃。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://news.nationalgeographic.com/news/2010/03/100310/why-tap-water-is-better/|title=Why Tap Water Is Better.|last=|first=|date=2010-03-13|website=National Geographic|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151109194813/http://news.nationalgeographic.com/news/2010/03/100310/why-tap-water-is-better/|archive-date=2015-11-09|accessdate=2015-11-29|df=|dead-url=no}}</ref>根据美国[[PET容器资源协会|PET容器资源协会]]的数据，自2013年以来，PET的回收率一直稳定在31％。<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.napcor.com/pdf/|title = 2014 U.S. PET container recycling rate holds at 31%|date = 2015-10-13|accessdate = 2015-10-25|website = National Association for PET Container Resources|publisher = |last = Moore|first = Rick|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151124163829/http://www.napcor.com/pdf/RRate2014_PR-FINAL.pdf|archivedate = 2015-11-24|df = |dead-url = no}}</ref>剩下的[[塑料污染|未回收]]PET塑料瓶散布在[[垃圾填埋场|垃圾填埋场]]，路边、海滩或河流和海洋中，总质量达到{{convert|4,000,000,000|lb|kg}}。而因为PET用作包装材料的特性（稳定性和耐用性）还使其在使用寿命结束后仍能很长时间无法分解。

虽然PET等聚酯可以通过[[水解|水解]]达到降解：此时PET分子中的[[酯#酯的水解|酯键]]会被水分子切断（反应在酸性或碱性条件下进行的方式有所不同，但都在200-300°C的温度下效果最佳），但在自然环境条件下，该过程缓慢到无法察觉的程度。
<ref>{{Cite journal|title = A review on the potential biodegradability of poly(ethylene terephthalate)|last = Kint*|first = Darwin|date = 1999|journal = Polymer International|volume = 48|issue = 5|pages = 346–352|doi = 10.1002/(SICI)1097-0126(199905)48:5<346::AID-PI156>3.0.CO;2-N|pmid = |df = }}</ref>

PET塑料被认为是不可降解塑料，用这种材料做出的[[塑料瓶|塑料瓶]]分解可能需要长达450年的时间。<ref>{{Cite web|title = Garbage Decomposition Time {{!}} Waste Segregation Guide|url = http://www.getwaste.info/garbage-decomposition-time/|website = www.getwaste.info|accessdate = 2015-11-29|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304083405/http://www.getwaste.info/garbage-decomposition-time/|archivedate = 2016-03-04|df = |dead-url = no}}</ref> 因此，市场上相应的出现了使用其他制作材料的水容器。

== 替代容器 ==
{{main|Ooho}}
“[[Ooho|Ooho]]”是一种凝胶状的双膜球，可以通过将冰滴入钙盐或[[海藻酸|海藻酸]]的溶液中制成。该过程称为{{link-en|Spherification}}，是[[联合利华|联合利华]]工程师威廉·佩沙特在1940年代获得专利的技术。最近，西班牙厨师{{link-en|费兰·阿德里亚|Ferran Adrià}}将这种方法引入现代主义烹饪中。该过程产生了可食用的，可生物降解的胶囊。

=== 海藻酸钙凝胶 ===
[[File:Sodium_alginate.svg|thumb]]
海藻酸盐是一种褐藻的天然产物，已广泛用于伤口敷料，药物输送和组织工程以及食品应用中。<ref>{{Cite journal|title = Development of two alginate-based wound dressings|journal = Journal of Materials Science: Materials in Medicine|date = 2008-02-12|issn = 0957-4530|pages = 2503–2513|volume = 19|issue = 6|doi = 10.1007/s10856-008-3389-2|pmid = 18266085|first = Chih-Tung|last = Chiu|first2 = Jui-Sheng|last2 = Lee|first3 = Chi-Shung|last3 = Chu|first4 = Yi-Pin|last4 = Chang|first5 = Yng-Jiin|last5 = Wang}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title = Alginate in Drug Delivery Systems|journal = Drug Development and Industrial Pharmacy|date = 2002-01-01|issn = 0363-9045|pmid = 12149954|pages = 621–630|volume = 28|issue = 6|doi = 10.1081/DDC-120003853|first = Hanne Hjorth|last = Tønnesen|first2 = Jan|last2 = Karlsen}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title = Cell-interactive Alginate Hydrogels for Bone Tissue Engineering|url = https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-dental-research_2001-11_80_11/page/2025|journal = Journal of Dental Research|date = 2001-11-01|issn = 0022-0345|pmid = 11759015|pages = 2025–2029|volume = 80|issue = 11|doi = 10.1177/00220345010800111501|first = E.|last = Alsberg|first2 = K. W.|last2 = Anderson|first3 = A.|last3 = Albeiruti|first4 = R. T.|last4 = Franceschi|first5 = D. J.|last5 = Mooney}}</ref>海藻酸钠是β-D-甘露糖醛酸（β-D-mannuronic，M）和α-L-古洛糖醛酸（α-L-guluronic，G）按（1→4）键连接而成的直链[[共聚物|共聚物]]。 

海藻酸钠（NaAlg）暴露于氯化钙时会凝结 (CaCl<sub>2</sub>) 然后形成[[海藻酸钙|海藻酸钙]] (CaAlg<sub>2</sub> ) 和氯化钠(NaCl), 反应方程式如下：

2NaAlg + CaCl<sub>2</sub> → CaAlg<sub>2</sub> + 2NaCl

=== 安全性和生物降解性 ===
海藻酸盐凝胶的生物相容性已被广泛研究，其食用安全性已得到充分确立。<ref>{{Cite journal|title = Alginate: Properties and biomedical applications|journal = Progress in Polymer Science|date = 2012-01-01|pmc = 3223967|pmid = 22125349|pages = 106–126|volume = 37|issue = 1|doi = 10.1016/j.progpolymsci.2011.06.003|first = Kuen Yong|last = Lee|first2 = David J.|last2 = Mooney}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title = CALCIUM ALGINATE - National Library of Medicine HSDB Database|url = http://toxnet.nlm.nih.gov/cgi-bin/sis/search/a?dbs+hsdb:@term+@DOCNO+1911|website = toxnet.nlm.nih.gov|accessdate = 2015-11-29|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20171115002058/https://toxnet.nlm.nih.gov/cgi-bin/sis/search/a?dbs+hsdb:@term+@DOCNO+1911|archivedate = 2017-11-15|df = |dead-url = no}}</ref> 自然上，[[多糖|多糖]]具有抗消化酶分解的能力，而藻酸盐分类为[[膳食纤维|膳食纤维]]。尽管被食用后，Ooho胶囊虽然不能被直接消化，但随着钙从凝胶基质中扩散出来，与上述反应相反，Ooho胶囊将逐渐分解。<ref>{{Cite journal|title = Degradation of Partially Oxidized Alginate and Its Potential Application for Tissue Engineering|journal = Biotechnology Progress|date = 2001-01-01|issn = 1520-6033|pages = 945–950|volume = 17|issue = 5|doi = 10.1021/bp010070p|pmid = 11587588|first = Kamal H.|last = Bouhadir|first2 = Kuen Yong|last2 = Lee|first3 = Eben|last3 = Alsberg|first4 = Kelly L.|last4 = Damm|first5 = Kenneth W.|last5 = Anderson|first6 = David J.|last6 = Mooney|df = }}</ref>方程式如下：

CaAlg<sub>2</sub>   + 2NaCl  →  2NaAlg + CaCl<sub>2</sub>

由于藻酸盐是单链聚合物，因此藻酸盐可通过多种化学反应解聚（分解成较小的单元）。酸和碱均可破坏甘露糖醛酸酯（M）和古洛糖酸酯（G）单体之间的联系。自由基氧化是藻酸盐在环境中降解的另一种方式。许多细菌会产生一种酶（藻酸盐裂解酶），该酶可将分子分解为单糖，可作为生物体的能源。<ref>{{Cite book|title = Polysaccharides and Polyamides in the Food Industry|last = Steinbüchel|first = Alexander|publisher = Wiley-Blackwell|year = 2005|isbn = 978-3-527-31345-7|location = |pages = 222}}</ref>

